msgid "Welcome to EduCenter"
msgstr "EduCenter'ga xush kelibsiz"

msgid "Master Your Skills with EduCenter"
msgstr "EduCenter bilan malakangizni oshiring"

msgid ""
"Join thousands of students learning advanced techniques in web development, "
"programming, and design."
msgstr ""
"Veb-dasturlash, dasturlash va dizayn bo'yicha ilg'or usullarni o'rganayotgan"
" minglab talabalarga qo'shiling."

msgid "Explore Courses"
msgstr "Kurslarni ko'rish"

msgid "Sign Up for Free"
msgstr "Bepul ro'yxatdan o'tish"

msgid "Expert Instructors"
msgstr "Malakali o'qituvchilar"

msgid "Learn directly from university academics and industry experts."
msgstr ""
"To'g'ridan-to'g'ri universitet akademiklari va soha mutaxassislaridan "
"o'rganing."

msgid "Modern Technologies"
msgstr "Zamonaviy texnologiyalar"

msgid ""
"Stay up to date with the latest advanced web frameworks like Django and "
"React."
msgstr ""
"Django va React kabi eng so'nggi ilg'or veb-freymvorklar bilan hamqadam "
"bo'ling."

msgid "Interactive Learning"
msgstr "Interaktiv ta'lim"

msgid ""
"Engage with dynamic content, coursework projects, and hands-on exercises."
msgstr ""
"Dinamik kontent, kurs loyihalari va amaliy mashg'ulotlar bilan "
"shug'ullaning."

msgid "Browse Courses"
msgstr "Kurslarni izlash"

msgid "Language"
msgstr "Til"

msgid "Hello,"
msgstr "Salom,"

msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "Boshqaruv paneli"

msgid "Logout"
msgstr "Chiqish"

msgid "Login"
msgstr "Tizimga kirish"

msgid "Sign Up"
msgstr "Ro'yxatdan o'tish"

msgid "Welcome Back"
msgstr "Xush kelibsiz"

msgid "Ready to level up,"
msgstr "Bilimingizni oshirishga tayyormisiz,"

msgid ""
"Dive back into your studies. Discover new advanced courses, or continue "
"mastering your current skills."
msgstr ""
"O'qishga qayting. Yangi ilg'or kurslarni kashf eting yoki joriy malakangizni"
" oshirishda davom eting."

msgid "My Dashboard"
msgstr "Mening panelim"

msgid "Why Choose EduCenter?"
msgstr "Nima uchun EduCenter?"

msgid "About Us"
msgstr "Biz haqimizda"

msgid "Courses"
msgstr "Kurslar"

msgid "Contact"
msgstr "Aloqa"

msgid "Contact Us"
msgstr "Biz bilan bog'lanish"

msgid "Tashkent, Uzbekistan"
msgstr "Toshkent, O'zbekiston"

msgid "All rights reserved."
msgstr "Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan."

msgid "What Our Students Say"
msgstr "Talabalarimiz nima deydi"

msgid ""
"The Python course was amazing! The practical projects really helped me build"
" a strong portfolio and land my first developer job."
msgstr ""
"Python kursi ajoyib edi! Amaliy loyihalar menga kuchli portfolio yaratishda "
"va birinchi ishimni topishda juda yordam berdi."

msgid ""
"Very clear explanations and the instructors are extremely responsive. I "
"highly recommend EduCenter to everyone!"
msgstr ""
"Juda aniq tushuntirishlar va o'qituvchilar doim yordamga tayyor. Men hammani"
" EduCenter'ni tanlashga chaqiraman!"

msgid ""
"Learning React here was a breeze. The interactive exercises make a huge "
"difference compared to just watching video lectures."
msgstr ""
"Bu yerda React'ni o'rganish juda oson kechdi. Interaktiv mashqlar faqat "
"video ko'rishdan ko'ra katta farq qiladi."

msgid ""
"EduCenter is the best platform I've used. The material is very up-to-date "
"with current industry standards."
msgstr ""
"EduCenter men foydalangan eng yaxshi platforma. O'quv materiallari hozirgi "
"bozor standartlariga juda mos keladi."

msgid ""
"Master advanced techniques in web development, programming, and design with "
"industry experts."
msgstr ""
"Veb dasturlash, dasturlash va dizayn bo'yicha ilg'or usullarni soha "
"mutaxassislari bilan o'zlashtiring."
